<div class="container">
    <section class="about-section">
        <h1>@ViewData["Title"]</h1>

        <p>
            Welcome to SiteMasters IT! We are a leading company specializing in IT solutions for the construction industry.
            Our mission is to leverage technology to streamline processes, improve efficiency, and help construction businesses
            achieve their goals with modern software tools and services.
        </p>

        <h2>Our Mission</h2>
        <p>
            At SiteMasters IT, we are committed to delivering top-quality software solutions that cater to the unique needs of
            the construction industry. We strive to make construction project management easier and more efficient through
            innovative, easy-to-use technology.
        </p>

        <h2>Our Team</h2>
        <p>
            Our team is composed of industry experts with extensive experience in both IT and construction. From developers
            to project managers, every member of our team brings valuable insights to ensure that our products meet the highest standards.
        </p>

        <h2>What We Offer</h2>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Construction Management Software:</strong> Tools designed to optimize project planning, tracking, and collaboration.</li>
            <li><strong>Mobile Applications:</strong> Mobile-friendly solutions to access real-time data and manage operations on-site.</li>
            <li><strong>Custom Solutions:</strong> Tailored software that addresses specific business needs and challenges.</li>
            <li><strong>Cloud Services:</strong> Secure cloud-based services for easy access and collaboration from anywhere.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Why Choose Us?</h2>
        <p>
            We understand the complexities and demands of the construction industry, and our solutions are designed with these
            challenges in mind. Our focus on usability, scalability, and security ensures that our clients are equipped with
            cutting-edge tools that meet their needs both today and in the future.
        </p>

        <h2>Contact Us</h2>
        <p>If you would like to learn more about SiteMasters IT or our services, feel free to get in touch with us:</p>
